whipple_cams.json - Stephen Fegan - 2024-12-26

Pixel positions, radii and neighbor map for Whipple cameras, extracted from
WhippleCams.h, a part of ChiLA. The cameras are keyed by the number of ADC
channels read out, which is larger than the number of pixels, each ADC having
twelve channels.
